Ur ppa$ awal i ijehliyen. Nna$ iten yis, amennu$ ameqwôan.
D Neppa i Issemfaôaqen sin ilellen, yiwen êlaw, d aéidan, wayev ôéag, d ameô$an. Irra, garasen, agadir, aêdid ur nepwazgar.
